sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as TransferController
    participant Idempotency as IdempotencyService
    participant Accounts as LockedAccountLoader
    participant Ledger as LedgerPostingUseCase
    participant Audit as AuditEventWriter
    participant Outbox as OutboxWriterService
    participant DB as Oracle

    Client->>API: POST /api/v1/transfers with Idempotency-Key
    API->>Idempotency: validate key and request hash
    Idempotency->>DB: read existing idempotency record
    alt same key and same body exists
        DB-->>Idempotency: stored response
        Idempotency-->>API: replay response
        API-->>Client: 200 stored response
    else new request
        API->>Accounts: lock source and destination accounts
        Accounts->>DB: SELECT FOR UPDATE in stable account order
        API->>Ledger: post balanced transfer journal
        Ledger->>DB: insert transaction, journal, postings, update cached balances
        API->>Audit: write transfer audit event
        Audit->>DB: insert audit event
        API->>Outbox: write ledger/account events
        Outbox->>DB: insert pending outbox events
        API->>Idempotency: store response
        Idempotency->>DB: insert idempotency record
        API-->>Client: 201 transfer response
    end
